<li>Transport for London (TfL) is investing &pound;10 billion over the next five years to improve and expand London's transport network, more than half of that in the Tube</li>
<li>Metronet are responsible for the maintenance and renewal of the Bakerloo, Central, Waterloo and City, Victoria, Metropolitan, Hammersmith and City, District, Circle and East London lines.<br></li></ul>

     

        
        
        
